	   <tr><td colspan=2>Expect a hard life on PvP. Several friends of mine and I started PvP players on Tal Zek.<br><br>We decided to go human team (barbarian, human, erudite) and so far have enjoyed it. I would say the easiest time went to my friend who choose a Erudite Magician. Next up would be my Human SK.<br><br>The hardest went to my Barbarian Shaman and Human Cleric friends. On the PvP's people tend not to be the most sociable. As such they don't like to share or aid you if your a support class, they tend to just 'expect help' while giving you nothing.<br><br>So you have been warned. While we are NOT the highest on the server (our level range, 5 of us total, is 21 to 37) we have experianced enough for me to give that warning.<br><br>Which is part of why i'm playing a Ogre Shaman on Val Zek now for our evil team characters... I want a challenge!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
