	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sure it is. I've seen the mid 50's tackled in a few days of hardcore leveling with a good group. <br><br>Get some friends around your level with a similiar goal (not more then one or two levels either way above or below) and arrange to meet everynight in a predsignated location. <br><br>Expect to put in 5-8 hours a night for 3-6 nights, but your levels CAN be hit in a week, it just takes a good group. By the second day you'll either be a good group... or you'll be dead. And if you made it to the low 50's, i'm guessing the former. Crappy players don't make it to the 50's often.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
